{"id":272,"parent_id":266,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":272,"title":"Revelation 6","subtitle":"","short_title":"Rev.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 6"],[".studySummary",["i","Christ opens the six seals, and John sees the events therein—In the fifth seal, he sees the Christian martyrs; and in the sixth, he sees the signs of the times."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.1","order":"03.29.006.27506"},["b","1"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"And"],"I saw when the Lamb opened one of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"seals"],", and I heard, as it were the noise of thunder, one of the four",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"beasts"],"saying, Come and see."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.2","order":"03.29.006.27507"},["b","2"],"And I saw, and behold a white horse: and he that sat on him had a bow; and a crown was given unto him: and he went forth conquering, and to conquer."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.3","order":"03.29.006.27508"},["b","3"],"And when he had opened the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"second"],"seal, I heard the second beast say, Come and see."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.4","order":"03.29.006.27509"},["b","4"],"And there went out another horse",["i","that was"],"red: and",["i","power"],"was given to him that sat thereon to take",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"peace"],"from the earth, and that they should kill one another: and there was given unto him a great sword."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.5","order":"03.29.006.27510"},["b","5"],"And when he had opened the third seal, I heard the third beast say, Come and see. And I beheld, and lo a black horse; and he that sat on him had a pair of balances in his hand."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.6","order":"03.29.006.27511"},["b","6"],"And I heard a voice in the midst of the four beasts say, A measure of wheat for a penny, and three measures of barley for a penny; and",["i","see"],"thou hurt not the oil and the wine."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.7","order":"03.29.006.27512"},["b","7"],"And when he had opened the fourth seal, I heard the voice of the fourth beast say, Come and see."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.8","order":"03.29.006.27513"},["b","8"],"And I looked, and behold a pale horse: and his name that sat on him was Death, and Hell followed with him. And power was given unto them over the fourth part of the earth, to kill with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"sword"],", and with hunger, and with death, and with the beasts of the earth."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.9","order":"03.29.006.27514"},["b","9"],"And when he had opened the fifth seal, I saw under the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"altar"],"the souls of them that were",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"slain"],"for the word of God, and for the testimony which they held:"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.10","order":"03.29.006.27515"},["b","10"],"And they cried with a loud voice, saying, How long, O Lord, holy and true, dost thou not judge and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"avenge"],"our blood on them that dwell on the earth?"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.11","order":"03.29.006.27516"},["b","11"],"And",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"white"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"robes"],"were given unto every one of them; and it was said unto them, that they should",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"rest"],"yet for a little season, until their fellowservants also and their brethren, that should be killed as they",["i","were,"],"should be fulfilled."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.12","order":"03.29.006.27517"},["b","12"],"And I beheld when he had opened the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"sixth seal"],", and, lo, there was a great",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"earthquake"],"; and the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_12c"},"sun"],"became",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_12d"},"black"],"as sackcloth of hair, and the moon became as",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_12e"},"blood"],";"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.13","order":"03.29.006.27518"},["b","13"],"And the stars of heaven fell unto the earth, even as a fig tree casteth her",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"untimely figs"],", when she is shaken of a mighty wind."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.14","order":"03.29.006.27519"},["b","14"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"And"],"the heaven departed as a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"scroll"],"when it is rolled together; and every",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"mountain"],"and island were moved out of their places."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.15","order":"03.29.006.27520"},["b","15"],"And the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"kings"],"of the earth, and the great men, and the rich men, and the chief captains, and the mighty men, and every bondman, and every free man, hid themselves in the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"dens"],"and in the rocks of the mountains;"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.16","order":"03.29.006.27521"},["b","16"],"And said to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"mountains"],"and rocks, Fall on us, and hide us from the face of him that sitteth on the throne, and from the wrath of the Lamb:"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.17","order":"03.29.006.27522"},["b","17"],"For the great",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"day"],"of his wrath is come; and who shall be able to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"stand"],"?"]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.1a","order":"03.29.006.27523"},["b","1a"],["span.small","JST"],"Rev. 6:1 And I saw when the Lamb opened one of the seals,",["i","one of the four beasts,"],"and I heard …"],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.1b","order":"03.29.006.27525"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/seal"},"TG Seal"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.1c","order":"03.29.006.27527"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/cherubim"},"TG Cherubim"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.3a","order":"03.29.006.27529"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/77.7"},"D&C 77:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/8.28.22,28-29"},"Moses 8:28 (22, 28–29)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.4a","order":"03.29.006.27531"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.35"},"D&C 1:35"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.8a","order":"03.29.006.27533"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.17"},"Ezek. 5:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.21"},"14:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.27"},"33:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.9a","order":"03.29.006.27535"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/135.7"},"D&C 135:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.9b","order":"03.29.006.27537"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/martyrdom"},"TG Martyrdom"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/persecution"},"Persecution"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.10a","order":"03.29.006.27539"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/32.43"},"Deut. 32:43"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.11a","order":"03.29.006.27541"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.4"},"Rev. 3:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.11b","order":"03.29.006.27543"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apparel"},"TG Apparel"],"."],["div",{"id":"11c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.11c","order":"03.29.006.27545"},["b","11c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/paradise"},"TG Paradise"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.12a","order":"03.29.006.27547"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/77.10"},"D&C 77:10"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/last-days"},"TG Last Days"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.12b","order":"03.29.006.27549"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.18"},"Rev. 16:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"12c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.12c","order":"03.29.006.27551"},["b","12c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/world-end-of"},"TG World, End of"],"."],["div",{"id":"12d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.12d","order":"03.29.006.27553"},["b","12d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/24.29"},"Matt. 24:29"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/45.42"},"D&C 45:42"],"."],["div",{"id":"12e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.12e","order":"03.29.006.27555"},["b","12e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.31"},"Joel 2:31"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.87"},"D&C 88:87"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.13a","order":"03.29.006.27557"},["b","13a"],["span.small","IE"],"figs that ripen late, hanging on the tree even into the winter."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.14a","order":"03.29.006.27559"},["b","14a"],["span.small","JST"],"Rev. 6:14 And the",["i","heavens opened"],"as a scroll",["i","is opened"],"when it is rolled together; and every mountain, and island,",["i","was"],"moved out of",["i","its place."]],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.14b","order":"03.29.006.27561"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.4"},"Isa. 34:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.95"},"D&C 88:95"],"."],["div",{"id":"14c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.14c","order":"03.29.006.27563"},["b","14c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.20.17-21"},"Rev. 16:20 (17–21)"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.15a","order":"03.29.006.27565"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/kings-earthly"},"TG Kings, Earthly"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.15b","order":"03.29.006.27567"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/2.19"},"Isa. 2:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.16a","order":"03.29.006.27569"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.8"},"Hosea 10:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/23.30.27-31"},"Luke 23:30 (27–31)"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.17a","order":"03.29.006.27571"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/day-of-the-lord"},"TG Day of the Lord"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-second-coming"},"Jesus Christ, Second Coming"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.17b","order":"03.29.006.27573"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/76.7"},"Ps. 76:7"],"."]]}
